4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of machine learning techniques such as descriptor learning and convolutional neural networks falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence.
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory): The paper's focus on generating stable space-time data sets for reusable repositories could be relevant to game development, which falls under the category of computer science and game theory.
